I
Our Story
“It all started with a dance.”
🍂
May 2022
It All Started With a Dance
Michael tried so hard to teach me how to dance. He asked why I didn’t dance with anyone, and I told him I never properly learned how to dance with a partner. Dancing with my mom in our kitchen wasn’t the same, and neither was dancing in my dad’s arms when I was little.
He laughed, and we talked like we were already friends.
July 26, 2025
His Version
When Michael was asked what he considered our first date, he said it was the day we went to the beach with my mom. A simple day by the water became part of the story in his heart.
February 8, 2026
A Place at the Table
Our first official date, to me, was at his house on Super Bowl Sunday. What made it special wasn’t the game. It was being surrounded by his parents, siblings, brother-in-law, and friends.
I got to see where Michael learned to love, and little by little, it felt like I was becoming part of his family too.
